      <h2>Understand the Exam Pattern</h2>
      <p>Though the number of questions is the same, the paper pattern differs for each college. Therefore, knowing the paper pattern for the particular college plays a vital role in qualifying for the entrance exam.</p>
    <p>As per the CUET Exam Pattern, the entrance exam will include four sections:
      <ul>
        <li>Section 1 A:13 Languages</li>
        <li>Section 1 B:19 Languages</li>
        <li>Section 2: Domain-specific test</li>
        <li>Section 3:General test</li>
      </ul>
    </p> 
